    <item>
      <title>兰博基尼首席执行​​官称其在插电式混合动力汽车领域“占据有利地位”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-04/lamborghini-ceo-on-record-year-hybrids-us-market-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[兰博基尼首席执行​​官 Stephan Winkelmann 表示，该汽车制造商有望在 2024 年创下交付量和营业利润创纪录的一年，并讨论了在其产品线中增加第四款车型、对混合动力汽车的关注，以及为什么他认为母公司大众实施的削减不会对该品牌产生负面影响。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-04/lamborghini-ceo-on-record-year-hybrids-us-market-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 18:03:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚亲欧盟政党同意组成联盟抵御极右翼势力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/romanian-pro-eu-parties-agree-coalition-to-stave-off-far-right</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚亲欧洲政党签署协议组建联合政府，试图在周日的总统选举第二轮投票之前阻止民族主义势力掌权，而亲俄候选人将是第二轮投票的领跑者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/romanian-pro-eu-parties-agree-coalition-to-stave-off-far-right</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 17:44:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>环球人寿股价因做空者声称“办公室空置”而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/globe-life-shares-sink-on-short-seller-s-empty-office-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名卖空者称，环球人寿保险公司 (Globe Life Inc.) 的美国收入人寿 (American Income Life) 部门似乎已经关闭了几家主要办事处，此后该公司股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/globe-life-shares-sink-on-short-seller-s-empty-office-claims</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 17:23:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国关闭俄罗斯加密货币富豪网络，转移寡头数十亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/crypto-rich-russian-networks-moving-oligarch-billions-shut-down-by-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国警方表示，他们已经关闭了俄罗斯网络，该网络通过在欧洲、中东和南美洲交换现金和加密货币，为寡头、街头帮派和间谍转移数十亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/crypto-rich-russian-networks-moving-oligarch-billions-shut-down-by-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
