      <title>交易取消后，Coach 所有者开始出售债券以偿还贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/tapestry-kicks-off-bond-sale-to-repay-loans-after-scrapped-deal</link>
